80
00:03:51,350 --> 00:03:53,200
How can we mistreat our swords?

81
00:03:53,510 --> 00:03:54,600
Didn't you just say

82
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:56,480
you'd stay in Tianqi City for a few more days?

83
00:03:56,830 --> 00:03:58,000
Three days later,

84
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,550
after you rest up,

85
00:03:59,790 --> 00:04:01,720
we'll come here again for a sword battle.

86
00:04:02,070 --> 00:04:02,350
I...

87
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:02,920
Mr. Luo,

88
00:04:03,510 --> 00:04:04,280
we'll excuse ourselves.

89
00:04:04,670 --> 00:04:05,720
See you in three days.

90
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:07,480
Let's go, hurry up.

91
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:08,630
Quickly.

92
00:04:19,310 --> 00:04:19,840
Quick.

93
00:04:20,350 --> 00:04:20,990
Come on.

94
00:04:22,350 --> 00:04:23,640
Lei Wujie, are you out of your mind?

95
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:25,600
How could you possibly fight him?

96
00:04:26,790 --> 00:04:27,480
Lei,

97
00:04:28,110 --> 00:04:29,550
