100
00:04:34,350 --> 00:04:36,350
After the two exciting showdowns,

101
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:37,600
Lone Sword Deity's radiance

102
00:04:37,750 --> 00:04:39,720
is outstanding among the swordsmen.

103
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:41,350
