105
00:04:43,110 --> 00:04:44,110
but no one came forward.

106
00:04:44,230 --> 00:04:45,430
Yet, Lei Wujie stepped forward

107
00:04:45,550 --> 00:04:46,870
and joked around.

108
00:04:46,990 --> 00:04:48,110
He even made a three-day covenant with him.

109
00:04:48,350 --> 00:04:49,960
The moment was totally ruined.

110
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:52,190
It caused Lone Sword Deity to fail

111
00:04:52,350 --> 00:04:54,230
in making it look like the master

112
00:04:54,350 --> 00:04:55,550
was seeking defeat.

113
00:04:56,310 --> 00:04:58,280
Miss Ye knows me well.

114
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:00,670
What about the fight three days later?

115
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:02,310
Lei Wujie, what will you do?

116
00:05:03,110 --> 00:05:04,520
I'm no match for any of the three persons

117
00:05:04,670 --> 00:05:06,080
in the battles today.

118
00:05:06,350 --> 00:05:07,080
Especially

119
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:08,040
the Lone Sword Deity, Luo Qingyang.

120
00:05:08,350 --> 00:05:09,960
We remain far apart.

121
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:11,480
So you know this.

122
00:05:11,750 --> 00:05:12,280
But he chopped off

123
00:05:12,430 --> 00:05:13,640
Lord Yong'an's plaque with his sword.

124
00:05:13,840 --> 00:05:14,920
He was trying to crack the whip.

125
00:05:15,550 --> 00:05:16,750
Whether we challenge him or not,

126
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:17,790
he'll come to us eventually.

127
00:05:18,350 --> 00:05:19,920
Rather than letting him start a fight,

128
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:21,720
why don't we take the initiative?

129
00:05:21,990 --> 00:05:23,400
At least we can...

130
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:26,400
What?

131
00:05:27,350 --> 00:05:29,110
We can make ourselves known.

132
00:05:32,350 --> 00:05:33,790
You're such a peculiar man.

133
00:05:36,110 --> 00:05:37,980
[Lord Bai's Residence]

134
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:38,870
You're fine.

135
00:05:39,430 --> 00:05:40,160
It's no big deal.

136
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:42,040
Just get some rest.

137
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,230
Thank you, sir.

138
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:44,430
Mr. Xie Xuan.

139
00:05:45,080 --> 00:05:45,750
Wushuang.

140
00:05:48,790 --> 00:05:49,400
Wushuang.

141
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,350
These

142
00:05:50,550 --> 00:05:52,160
are the best tonics I got

