146
00:05:56,310 --> 00:05:58,080
It's not easy to get these.

147
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,110
You're here to ask for advice.

148
00:06:00,310 --> 00:06:00,990
Cut the crap.

149
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:01,790
Just get to the point.

150
00:06:02,190 --> 00:06:04,600
Are you trying to ask about Luo Qingyang's sword?

151
00:06:05,550 --> 00:06:06,350
Yes.

152
00:06:06,670 --> 00:06:08,640
As the saying goes, know thy self,

153
00:06:08,790 --> 00:06:09,960
know thy enemy.

154
00:06:10,310 --> 00:06:11,920
Well, I can't make my sword technique

155
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:13,840
stronger than his in such a short time.

156
00:06:13,990 --> 00:06:14,720
But

157
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:15,960
I have to look for his weakness

158
00:06:16,110 --> 00:06:16,840
in his sword technique.

159
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,230
So I can start with his weakness,

160
00:06:18,430 --> 00:06:20,160
launch a surprise attack,
and defeat him in one hit.

161
00:06:20,350 --> 00:06:20,960
Okay.

162
00:06:21,110 --> 00:06:21,790
Go ahead.

163
00:06:24,990 --> 00:06:26,110
Here's my question.

164
00:06:27,230 --> 00:06:28,600
From which direction

165
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:31,310
did his final sword attack you?

166
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:32,920
It was from all directions.

167
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:35,400
Okay.

168
00:06:36,080 --> 00:06:36,670
Well,

169
00:06:36,960 --> 00:06:37,790
at that time,

170
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:41,160
which part of his sword qi was the strongest

171
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:43,480
and which was the weakest?

172
00:06:44,310 --> 00:06:45,310
It was everywhere.

173
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,960
There's nothing to say, then.

174
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:49,190
It was how I felt.

175
00:06:49,750 --> 00:06:50,960
Having a sword fight

176
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:52,670
with Luo Qingyang is different.

177
00:06:53,070 --> 00:06:54,820
We were standing there.

178
00:06:55,140 --> 00:06:56,110
But it felt like

179
00:06:56,380 --> 00:06:58,020
I was in a brand-new place.

180
00:06:58,630 --> 00:06:59,310
That place

181
00:06:59,460 --> 00:07:00,580
belonged to Luo Qingyang.

182
00:07:00,820 --> 00:07:01,510
No.

183
00:07:01,950 --> 00:07:02,950
It belonged to Luo Qingyang's

184
00:07:03,110 --> 00:07:04,070
Nine-Song Sword Technique.

185
00:07:04,870 --> 00:07:05,990
The wind was desolate.

186
00:07:06,380 --> 00:07:07,700
It was a boundless field.

187
00:07:08,190 --> 00:07:09,110
I vaguely heard

188
00:07:09,260 --> 00:07:11,190
someone singing in my ears.

189
00:07:11,780 --> 00:07:14,780
And for a moment, I wanted to cry.

190
00:07:15,580 --> 00:07:16,630
This is so-called

191
00:07:16,630 --> 00:07:17,870
the sword deity's sword tendency.

192
00:07:19,260 --> 00:07:20,220
With a swing,

193
00:07:20,380 --> 00:07:21,510
he can create a brand new place.

194
00:07:21,700 --> 00:07:22,750
In that place,

195
00:07:22,990 --> 00:07:24,220
he's the ruler.

196
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:25,820
Is there any way

197
00:07:25,870 --> 00:07:27,630
to break the sword deity's sword tendency?

198
00:07:29,950 --> 00:07:30,870
Every sword deity

199
00:07:31,190 --> 00:07:32,780
has its own sword tendency.

200
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:35,580
It's like a small world.

201
00:07:35,820 --> 00:07:37,580
If you want to break this small world,

202
00:07:37,950 --> 00:07:39,820
instead of doing what the sword wants,

203
00:07:40,110 --> 00:07:42,220
you have to do the other.

204
00:07:43,220 --> 00:07:44,340
The sword tendency

205
00:07:44,340 --> 00:07:46,340
of Lone Sword Deity gives a sense of melancholy.

206
00:07:48,020 --> 00:07:49,630
I got it.

207
00:07:51,140 --> 00:07:52,340
You learn fast.

208
00:07:52,670 --> 00:07:54,140
You're quite smart.

209
00:07:54,780 --> 00:07:55,630
What is the solution?

210
00:07:57,430 --> 00:07:59,110
I'll scold him.

211
00:08:01,510 --> 00:08:04,020
The sword tendency is the crucial part
of the desolate sword.

212
00:08:04,870 --> 00:08:05,820
Once the Martyr Sword is drawn,

213
00:08:06,020 --> 00:08:07,220
the desolate wind blows.

214
00:08:07,380 --> 00:08:09,020
It's the time when the warriors sing.

215
00:08:09,460 --> 00:08:10,430
This is when the tension rises.

216
00:08:10,750 --> 00:08:11,700
I go on a rampage and yell,

217
00:08:13,220 --> 00:08:14,140
"Luo Qingyang,

218
00:08:14,310 --> 00:08:15,550
you old man!

219
00:08:15,780 --> 00:08:16,750
Why did you come

220
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:17,900
to Tianqi City

221
00:08:18,070 --> 00:08:18,870
