222
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:19,750
What has

223
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:20,990
Tianqi City got to do with you?

224
00:08:21,220 --> 00:08:21,990
Why have you

225
00:08:22,140 --> 00:08:23,190
chosen to come at this time?

226
00:08:23,380 --> 00:08:24,510
You held sword fights at Tianqi.

227
00:08:24,670 --> 00:08:25,670
Did Tianqi City agree on it?

228
00:08:25,820 --> 00:08:27,110
You even crashed the plaque.

229
00:08:27,310 --> 00:08:28,670
Do you know how expensive the plaque is?

230
00:08:28,870 --> 00:08:29,990
Just get lost!"

231
00:08:32,270 --> 00:08:32,910
Mr. Xie Xuan.

232
00:08:33,430 --> 00:08:34,580
As I yell at him like this,

233
00:08:35,460 --> 00:08:36,980
do you think he'll still be able

234
00:08:37,220 --> 00:08:38,460
to create an aura of melancholy?

235
00:08:40,310 --> 00:08:41,860
Actually, about what you said,

236
00:08:42,270 --> 00:08:43,030
I think

237
00:08:43,310 --> 00:08:44,620
it's got some points.

238
00:08:47,430 --> 00:08:48,190
Mr. Xie,

239
00:08:48,860 --> 00:08:49,460
you don't have to

240
00:08:49,670 --> 00:08:50,910
care about this fool's feelings.

241
00:08:51,190 --> 00:08:52,100
Just tell the truth.

242
00:08:52,550 --> 00:08:53,670
I'm not comforting him.

243
00:08:54,430 --> 00:08:55,150
If we do

244
00:08:55,150 --> 00:08:56,860
as Lei said,

245
00:08:57,390 --> 00:08:59,100
that desolate sword tendency

246
00:08:59,340 --> 00:09:01,150
will indeed be easily thwarted.

247
00:09:02,220 --> 00:09:02,910
Of course.

248
00:09:03,270 --> 00:09:04,150
You can yell at him.

249
00:09:04,430 --> 00:09:06,500
But it only plays a supporting role.

250
00:09:06,700 --> 00:09:07,430
It's impossible

251
00:09:07,620 --> 00:09:09,550
to defeat a sword deity like this.

252
00:09:09,740 --> 00:09:10,430
Don't you think?

253
00:09:11,670 --> 00:09:12,550
By the way,

254
00:09:14,150 --> 00:09:15,740
the Sword Heart Technique

255
00:09:15,980 --> 00:09:18,310
of your family is about honing the sword heart.

256
00:09:18,950 --> 00:09:20,700
If you could cultivate in seclusion for two days

257
00:09:20,910 --> 00:09:23,220
and practice the technique
with the pure sword heart.

258
00:09:23,500 --> 00:09:24,980
You might have a window of opportunity.

259
00:09:26,190 --> 00:09:27,100
You're right.

260
00:09:27,430 --> 00:09:28,550
I'm thinking about this too.

261
00:09:29,500 --> 00:09:30,860
Well, we'll excuse ourselves.

262
00:09:31,070 --> 00:09:32,670
Sir, please come and watch the fight

263
00:09:32,980 --> 00:09:33,950
three days later.

264
00:09:36,180 --> 00:09:37,670
[Snowfall Villa]

265
00:09:37,670 --> 00:09:38,340
Xiao Se,

266
00:09:38,740 --> 00:09:39,980
I'll name the sword technique of mine

267
00:09:40,190 --> 00:09:41,220
as Insulting Sword Technique,

268
00:09:41,430 --> 00:09:42,670
what do you think?

269
00:09:43,270 --> 00:09:43,860
I defeat

270
00:09:44,030 --> 00:09:45,270
the sword deity while insulting him.

271
00:09:45,550 --> 00:09:46,740
