274
00:09:50,580 --> 00:09:52,030
You're a good writer, help me with it.

275
00:09:52,270 --> 00:09:53,220
Do you have any idea

276
00:09:53,390 --> 00:09:54,790
what kind of an opponent you're facing?

277
00:09:55,340 --> 00:09:56,500
He's the number one swordsman

278
00:09:56,670 --> 00:09:57,820
on the Top-Rank List,

279
00:09:57,980 --> 00:09:58,910
the one-of-a-kind master

280
00:09:59,070 --> 00:10:00,030
who's as good as Baili Dongjun.

281
00:10:01,220 --> 00:10:02,390
That's why I need two days

282
00:10:02,550 --> 00:10:03,620
to focus on cultivating my sword.

283
00:10:04,030 --> 00:10:04,820
By the way,

284
00:10:05,700 --> 00:10:06,500
Xiao Se,

285
00:10:07,030 --> 00:10:07,860
yesterday, I only said

286
00:10:08,060 --> 00:10:09,150
