299
00:10:28,670 --> 00:10:29,340
Go on.

300
00:10:29,910 --> 00:10:30,580
This way.

301
00:10:34,270 --> 00:10:35,220
He wants to obtain the sword heart?

302
00:10:35,820 --> 00:10:36,460
Yes.

303
00:10:37,100 --> 00:10:38,430
