00:11:12,700 --> 00:11:13,700
In this regard,

325
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:14,980
I guess Luo Qingyang

326
00:11:15,070 --> 00:11:16,390
won't kill him.

327
00:11:17,220 --> 00:11:18,190
This silly guy

328
00:11:18,700 --> 00:11:20,390
knew that he'd suffer.

329
00:11:22,580 --> 00:11:23,620
Perhaps this fight

330
00:11:24,790 --> 00:11:26,190
will do him good.

