335
00:11:39,790 --> 00:11:40,790
to kill Xiao Se

336
00:11:41,190 --> 00:11:42,460
in Tianqi City?

337
00:11:43,700 --> 00:11:44,580
Xiao Se doesn't want others

338
00:11:44,740 --> 00:11:46,190
