450
00:15:53,060 --> 00:15:55,060
I heard that the Wrathful Sword Deity

451
00:15:55,060 --> 00:15:56,700
and the City Lord of Wushuang City

452
00:15:56,890 --> 00:15:58,100
were defeated.

453
00:15:58,700 --> 00:15:59,650
Yes.

