00:16:00,420 --> 00:16:02,420
So I'm going to the Directorate of Astronomy

455
00:16:02,650 --> 00:16:04,610
to ask him to open
the Heavenly Sword Pavilion for me.

456
00:16:05,130 --> 00:16:06,300
Are you going to ask for a sword?

457
00:16:06,770 --> 00:16:07,420
That's right.

458
00:16:08,770 --> 00:16:09,580
The people think

