00:18:00,380 --> 00:18:02,180
But he didn't make that door.

508
00:18:02,940 --> 00:18:04,010
Because even if

509
00:18:04,220 --> 00:18:05,570
he made the door,

510
00:18:05,980 --> 00:18:07,620
he still couldn't make the thing

