534
00:19:38,330 --> 00:19:39,290
Life-Destroyer,

535
00:19:39,620 --> 00:19:40,420
Wind-Breaker,

536
00:19:40,780 --> 00:19:42,150
Dragon-Shocker, and Sky-Crusher.

