00:20:17,780 --> 00:20:19,060
About the thing I want,

550
00:20:19,630 --> 00:20:21,390
you should know better than anyone else.

551
00:20:25,980 --> 00:20:27,540
Even Lord Langya

552
00:20:28,150 --> 00:20:29,700
couldn't open this door

553
00:20:29,740 --> 00:20:30,740
back then.

554
00:20:31,740 --> 00:20:32,870
In terms of the sword technique,

555
00:20:33,430 --> 00:20:35,150
